title: ホーム
layout: layouts/base
pagination:
  data: collections.articles
  size: 5
  alias: articlesPage
permalink: "{% if pagination.pageNumber == 0 %}/{% else %}/page-{{ pagination.pageNumber + 1 }}/{% endif %}"
---

## 公開記事

{% if collections.articles | length > 0 %}

### 最新の記事 

{% for article in articlesPage %}
- **[{{ article.data.title }}]({{ article.url }})** — {{ article.data.publishedAt | dateISO }}
  {% if article.data.tags %}
  _Tags: {{ article.data.tags | join(", ") }}_
  {% endif %}
{% endfor %}

---

## ページネーション

<nav aria-label="Pagination">
  <div style="display: flex; gap: 1rem; justify-content: center; margin: 2rem 0; flex-wrap: wrap;">
    {% if pagination.previousPageHref %}
      <a href="{{ pagination.previousPageHref }}" class="btn" rel="prev">← 前のページ</a>
    {% endif %}
    
    <div style="display: flex; gap: 0.5rem; align-items: center; flex-wrap: wrap; justify-content: center;">
      {% for page in pagination.pages %}
        {% if loop.index0 == pagination.pageNumber %}
          <span aria-current="page" style="padding: 0.5rem 0.75rem; background: #0066cc; color: white; border-radius: 4px; font-weight: bold;">
            {{ loop.index }}
          </span>
        {% else %}
          <a href="{{ page }}" style="padding: 0.5rem 0.75rem; border: 1px solid #0066cc; border-radius: 4px; text-decoration: none; color: #0066cc;">
            {{ loop.index }}
          </a>
        {% endif %}
      {% endfor %}
    </div>
    
    {% if pagination.nextPageHref %}
      <a href="{{ pagination.nextPageHref }}" class="btn" rel="next">次のページ →</a>
    {% endif %}
  </div>
  
  <p style="text-align: center; color: #666; font-size: 0.9rem;">
    ページ {{ pagination.pageNumber + 1 }} / {{ pagination.pages | length }}（全 {{ collections.articles | length }} 件）
  </p>
</nav>

---

